Medical Affairs Associate MEA
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/01 07:20:03
Ref. JB3046181
Job Description
Immediate vacancy -
Qualified physician preferably working in oncology as a medical affairs associate/ scientific Liaison or advisor for multinational pharmaceutical company expanding in the region.
Skills
The role is based in Dubai at the Middle East hub in modern and
new offices. Don’t delay, join my client now while it is expanding in the region.
The role will report into the Medical Director
and is field based. It is essential you have a good strategic mindset and take active interest in all competitor publications and promotional activities.
It is essential you have excellent project managements skills along with very good communications skills both written and verbal. Fluent in English and ideally Arabic.
Previous working knowledge of training internal teams on disease areas to company related products. Actively holding round table discussion and attending company events.
The successful candidate with have good level of maturity to their work and have a learned investigative mind. Good career potential awaits you at this company.
My client will only consider those already working in a
similar role for a multinational pharmaceutical company within the region.
Education
Medical Degree
